hu.trigary.iodine.api.gui.container.base

Interface GuiContainer<T extends GuiContainer<T>>

  • Type Parameters:
    T - the class implementing this interface
    All Superinterfaces:
    AttachmentHolder<T>, DrawPrioritizeable<T>, GuiElement<T>, GuiParent<T>
    All Known Subinterfaces:
    GridGuiContainer, LinearGuiContainer

    public interface GuiContainer<T extends GuiContainer<T>>
extends GuiElement<T>, GuiParent<T>
    Represents a GuiElement that can contain other elements. A notable GuiParent that is not a subclass of this class is IodineGui.
